</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="out">out_values</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para><ref refid="struct_m_l_audio_spectral_analysis" kindref="compound">MLAudioSpectralAnalysis</ref> struct to be filled with the results properties.</para>
